            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">OTP Input has five interaction states controlling borders, shadows, and text colors.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
