                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">Verify identity via a numeric code sent by SMS, email, or authenticator app.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For 2FA (two-factor authentication) flows.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">For PIN entry where each digit is individually confirmed.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e42527" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>When NOT to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For passwords &#8212; use a password input field instead.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For codes longer than 6 digits &#8212; use a single text input with <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">inputmode="numeric"</code>.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">For alphanumeric codes &#8212; extend the component or use a standard text input.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Choosing Length / Size -->
